<h1>U.C.Engine Demonstrator.</h1>

<p>U.C.Engine (Unified Collaboration Engine), is an open source publish/subscribe server with persistence. It allows you to build real time applications like collaboration based services, live meetings, games or anything that fits well in an event driven philosophy.</p>

<p>This simple application based on U.C.Engine demonstrate what you can easily achieve with the framework. It provides a collaborative workspace with several interactive widgets. You can try to upload and share a pdf document, chat with other users and translate in realtime, share your video stream...</p>

<p>If you want to learn more we will be pleased so see you on the <a href="http://ucengine.org/">project website.</a></p>
